ingredient: 2 cups cooked bulgur, quinoa, couscous, or rice (chilled)
1.5 lb chicken thighs, boneless and skinless
2 cups long grain white rice, rinsed
1/2 cup frozen or fresh sweet cherries
4 cups finely shredded or chopped cabbage
2 Tbsp canola or vegetable oil, divided
1 tsp salt (to salt the boiling water)
